{
  "stem": "26142.13",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they gave them shovels and, and picks and, and wheelbarrows and for digging up mountains and filling in, in valleys.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so we stayed there in Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We stayed there for about-- in my, my group, where I, I was, we stayed there for about six weeks, six or eight weeks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it so happened that my brother Tsvi was also in a, in another camp, but also sent over there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I, I found him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But he was in, he fell into a very bad, bad group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I, I, our group was-- it all depended on the commander of the group.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If the commander was a half-decent person, he treated you half-decently.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I went to see him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And one day, we marched out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I saw him marching out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was always usually-- and he too, because he was tall just like me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I, I was always in the front, in the front of the line-- the taller, smaller.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know how the military do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And, and so I, I always had a front view.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was seeing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I saw, we saw each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we couldn't even get out to say goodbye to each other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that was the last time-- sometimes in, in, in August of 19, 1943, that was the last time we saw each other.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was later shipped out deeper into, into Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was sent to Bor That I found out later, that he was sent to Bor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we were sent back to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were assigned between Budapest and, and [INAUDIBLE] .",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "This is a city that the rail line was-- this was a one of the main lines that, that supplies to the, to the war front, was sent to.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
